{"tid":2419346,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首餵早產B 母︰佢有鬥志好叻抗爭","createTime":"2021-02-23T09:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T09:14:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8fcd292b3eaa63a729605fc5b79aa5b80414fe","tid":2419346,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:05:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210223/KPM4LLLZ4ZAMFCPND7TCTWZLL4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210223%2FKPM4LLLZ4ZAMFCPND7TCTWZLL4%2F&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv3xnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=00422fc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210223%2FKPM4LLLZ4ZAMFCPND7TCTWZLL4%2F&h=b3cd8d59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210223/KPM4LLLZ4ZAMFCPND7TCTWZLL4/</a><br />\n<br />\n首餵早產B 母︰佢有鬥志好叻抗爭<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「見到BB咁艱難都捱過咗，我更加唔可以放棄，追究警方到底！」42歲劉女士上月20日在土瓜灣遇警截查，稱被辱罵「死肥婆」並反鎖雙手，疑受驚過度引致早產，今日是兒子滿月，劉女士昨午往醫院探望，首次親手餵奶，她熱淚盈眶，堅持要向警方討回公道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Td4Esxb2whV9fMPV04XGKhco8vw=/1181x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OOUQDT36MVGFJACBJQVDNX6NR4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTd4Esxb2whV9fMPV04XGKhco8vw%3D%2F1181x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOOUQDT36MVGFJACBJQVDNX6NR4.jpg&h=a95cb2a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■兒子進展良好，已轉往新生嬰兒病房。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受子啟發 誓向警究責<br />\n<br />\nBB因不足月出世，出生後被送入氧氣箱，插滿喉管，劉女士終日以淚洗面。事隔一個月，BB進展良好，前日已轉往新生嬰兒加護病房，不再使用呼吸機及插喉輸奶，體重增至1.8公斤。<br />\n<br />\n昨午3時許，劉女士帶同新衣及棉被往醫院探望，但院方指暫不宜抱，不過准許劉餵奶。她憶述，手持奶樽餵B時，望着小生命啜奶十分感動。劉表示，感覺兒子生命頑強，一步步茁壯起來，希望他「越嚟越好快啲出嚟」，更「覺得BB好有鬥志，好叻抗爭咁」，她受兒子啟發，指不會退縮。上周五她往警署就涉嫌阻差辦公續保，被困了數小時，案件至今未有進展，但她會堅持到底，誓要討回公道，下月中再報到。<br />\n<br />\n劉女士連日為BB滿月張羅，準備新衣、豬腳薑及紅雞蛋，不少親友封了利是給他。為了探望BB，她每星期需檢測一次，取得陰性報告。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xck7AzSLdrdkfzFmiDbl_Mau3xc=/1578x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6UXXDL5OANE7RHDSDMO2S6PRY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fxck7AzSLdrdkfzFmiDbl_Mau3xc%3D%2F1578x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6UXXDL5OANE7RHDSDMO2S6PRY4.jpg&h=f6224d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉女士連日為兒子張羅新衣。"},{"pid":"8f295960ce9bf2f109fc6a6f287d3409613148e3","tid":2419346,"uid":81684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"唔會鬧佢 都唔會幸災樂禍<br />\n既然個呀媽知錯能改 咁我祝佢bb身體健康"},{"pid":"5f41133f21d6714892e9d09169dfa62557e7af09","tid":2419346,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"就睇下一個由藍轉黃既人會堅持到幾耐"}]}